 Documents       .ssh
 Downloads       .sudo_as_admin_successful
 .gitconfig      Templates
 .gnupg          Videos
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
2.rename - Rename all *.txt files to *.html

~/1Sunbeam Dac/OS/Practice/one$ ls
111.txt  11.txt  1.txt  two

~/1Sunbeam Dac/OS/Practice/one$ rename 's/txt/html/' *.txt

~/1Sunbeam Dac/OS/Practice/one$ ls
111.html  11.html  1.html  two

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
3.ln -s - Create symbolic link (shortcut) for a file
ln -s 1.html s.html 
111.html  11.html  1.html  s.html  two

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
4.ln Create hard link for a file
ln 11.html 11.txt
111.html  11.html  11.txt  1.html  s.html  two

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
