7.touch - Create empty file
ls
111.html  11.html  11.txt  1.html  s.html  two

~/1Sunbeam Dac/OS/Practice/one$ touch emp.txt

~/1Sunbeam Dac/OS/Practice/one$ ls
111.html  11.html  11.txt  1.html  emp.txt  s.html  two

