28.tr - Convert file contents into uppercase , also learn "-s" option of this command
cat emp.txt | tr 'a-z' 'A-z'
Puja
Swara
Snehal
Diksha
Pratiksha
Priya
Rupali
Pooja
Ashu
Aakash
Chaitnya
Satwik 
Omkar
Rushikesh
Aadesh
Payal

echo "DAC    PG" | tr -s " "
DAC PG

