29.cut Split the file contents using delimiter and print required fields
cat course.txt
PGDAC - JAVA DSA .NET C C++
PGDMC - JAVA DSA WPT JAVA-A REACT
PGDESD - PYTHON HADOOP JAVA 

cat course.txt | cut -d " " -f2,3,4
- JAVA DSA
- JAVA DSA
- PYTHON HADOOP

















